Dimension Data has announced its new executive leadership team to lead the Middle East and African (MEA) region. This follows the formation of NTT Ltd as a global group, while Dimension Data and its subsidiaries will represent the NTT brand within the Middle East and Africa. The company said the new executive team has been structured to execute on the company’s strategic agenda to enable growth and scalability. Jeremy Ord remains in his role as executive chairman of this business while Moss Ngoasheng is the deputy independent, non-executive chairman. Here is the full Dimension Data Middle East and African executive leadership team. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-312939" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Grant-Bodley.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Grant-Bodley.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Grant-Bodley-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Grant-Bodley-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-214830" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Saki-Missaikos-Internet-Solutions.jpg" alt="Saki Missaikos – Internet Solutions" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Saki-Missaikos-Internet-Solutions.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Saki-Missaikos-Internet-Solutions-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Saki-Missaikos-Internet-Solutions-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-312989" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Barry-Curtin.jpg" alt="" widt