oads/2019/07/Tony-Walt-1-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Tony-Walt-1-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-312941" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Setumo-Mohapi.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Setumo-Mohapi.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Setumo-Mohapi-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Setumo-Mohapi-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-312999" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/George-Todd-1.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/George-Todd-1.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/George-Todd-1-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/George-Todd-1-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />